sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (ext-proc)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Sidecar as P/D Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prefill as Prefill Worker<br/>varies/TCP
    participant Decoder as Local Decoder<br/>8001/TCP
    participant KVMgr as KV Cache Manager<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Standard Inference (Non-P/D)
    Client->>Envoy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC/9002 (plaintext)
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool/Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA Token)
    Note over EPP: Apply filters → scorers<br/>Select optimal pod
    EPP-->>Envoy: Routing decision<br/>(selected pod endpoint)
    Envoy->>vLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
    vLLM-->>Envoy: Inference response
    Envoy-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated P/D (NIXL v2)
    Client->>Envoy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC/9002 (plaintext)
    Note over EPP: P/D profile handler<br/>selects decode + prefill pods
    EPP-->>Envoy: Route to decoder pod<br/>+ prefill target header
    Envoy->>Sidecar: Forward to decoder<br/>HTTPS/8000 (TLS 1.2+)
    Note over Sidecar: SSRF validation<br/>Check allowlist
    Sidecar->>Prefill: Prefill stage<br/>HTTP or HTTPS (varies)
    Prefill-->>Sidecar: Prefill complete<br/>(KV cache transferred)
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Decode stage<br/>HTTP/8001
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming tokens
    Sidecar-->>Envoy: Response stream<br/>HTTPS/8000
    Envoy-->>Client: Streaming response

    Note over KVMgr,EPP: Flow 3: KV-Events for Precise Prefix Cache
    KVMgr->>EPP: KV cache state updates<br/>ZMQ/5557 (plaintext)
    Note over EPP: Update prefix cache index<br/>Use for scoring decisions
